text: Fabian Thylmann (born June 5, 1978, in Aachen) is a German entrepreneur. He got well-known, because he started in the porn business. From 2010, he has been at the head of Aylo (formerly Manwin), in Luxembourg. Aylo runs different porn sites, amongst others, YouPorn. In 2013, Thylmann sold Manwin and stepped down from his post. Today, he runs a club and a restaurant in Cologne, amongst others. Category:German businesspeople Category:1978 births Category:Living people
title: Fabian Thylmann
